---
import Site from '../../../layouts/Site.astro';
---
<Site title={'terms — rega rega'}>
<Fragment set:html={'<section class="doc-wrap">\n  <div class="meta-line"><span class="dot"></span>— terms of use</div>\n  <h1>how we <em>work</em> together.</h1>\n  <div class="updated">— updated may 2026 · jurisdiction georgia</div>\n\n  <p class="lede">By using bre.ge — browsing, contacting us, or booking through us — you agree to a few common-sense things. <b>We promise to be straight with you; we expect the same back.</b></p>\n\n  <h2>what bre.ge is</h2>\n  <p>bre is a small Batumi-based operator running short and mid-term rental apartments. We list our own managed apartments, maintain the Batumi guide, and offer property management services. The website is informational and lets you contact us to book or work together.</p>\n\n  <h2>bookings</h2>\n  <p>When you book through us — via Telegram, email, the contact form, or any other channel — you enter a rental agreement directly with us (or the property owner we represent). Terms of each booking — price, dates, deposit, cancellation policy — are confirmed in writing before the stay.</p>\n  <p>You may also book our apartments through Airbnb, Booking.com or Суточно. In that case, their terms apply on top of ours, and the booking is between you and the platform.</p>\n\n  <h2>your responsibilities</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>treat the apartment, neighbors and building with care</li>\n    <li>tell us the truth about who\'s staying and for how long</li>\n    <li>cover any damage caused during your stay</li>\n    <li>follow Georgian law during your stay</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>our responsibilities</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>describe apartments honestly — photos match reality</li>\n    <li>be reachable during your stay</li>\n    <li>fix problems quickly when they come up</li>\n    <li>respect your privacy as described in our <a href="/georgia/batumi/privacy" style="color:var(--page);font-weight:600">privacy policy</a></li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>cancellations &amp; refunds</h2>\n  <p>Cancellation terms depend on the channel and length of stay. For direct bookings, we usually offer flexible terms — exact rules are confirmed with the booking confirmation. For Airbnb/Booking.com bookings, the platform\'s rules apply.</p>\n\n  <h2>the guide</h2>\n  <p>Our Batumi guide is opinion, not legal advice. Restaurants, places and businesses we recommend are independent — we don\'t control their hours, prices, quality, or whether they\'re still open. We do our best to keep things current.</p>\n\n  <h2>limitations</h2>\n  <p>We\'re a small operator doing our best. We\'re not liable for things outside our control — power outages, water cuts, force majeure, decisions of building management or local authorities. If something goes wrong, we\'ll work with you to find a solution.</p>\n\n  <h2>changes</h2>\n  <p>We may update these terms. If we change anything significant, we\'ll update the date and notify anyone we have an active booking with.</p>\n\n  <h2>governing law</h2>\n  <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Georgia. Disputes that can\'t be resolved by talking it out go to Georgian courts.</p>\n\n  <div class="end">Have a question about a booking or these terms? Write us at <a href="mailto:hello@bre.ge">hello@bre.ge</a> or in <a href="https://t.me/bre_ge">Telegram</a>.</div>\n</section>'} />
<style is:global set:html={'.doc-wrap{padding:140px 28px 80px;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto}\n.meta-line{font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:500;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:24px}\n.meta-line .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--page)}\n.doc-wrap .updated{margin-top:18px;font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.doc-wrap .lede{margin-top:32px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.doc-wrap .lede b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}\n.doc-wrap h2{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:24px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-top:48px;text-transform:lowercase}\n.doc-wrap p{margin-top:14px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.doc-wrap p b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}\n.doc-wrap ul{margin-top:14px;padding-left:0;list-style:none}\n.doc-wrap ul li{padding-left:18px;position:relative;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:8px}\n.doc-wrap ul li::before{content:\'—\';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--page)}\n.doc-wrap .end{margin-top:64px;padding:24px;background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}\n.doc-wrap .end a{color:var(--page);font-weight:600}\n@media (max-width:880px){\n.doc-wrap{padding:100px 14px 48px}\n}'}></style>
</Site>
